short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Helper for syncing with Backstage Github issues

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is meant to be used by maintainers of open-source Backstage project so they can open in the browser all the latest issues that were created or updated in a certain period. This extension requires that you authorize access to your GitHub account to read repos data.

The open-source Backstage repository can be found here:
https://github.com/backstage/backstage
